Malibu Joe.
   The money is pouring in as the community mourns the Labor Day
weekend beating death of the 96-year-old Joe, who chose to live in
the bushes behind a Texaco gas station.
   Flowers and cards have been placed around the tiny
shrub-surrounded area Joe called home, and Miss MacGraw has joined
