2,100.64, closing above 2,100 for the first time since it stood at
2,107.40 on Aug. 8.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declines by nearly 2 to 1 on the
NYSE, with 969 up, 493 down and 488 unchanged.
   Big Board volume totaled 177.22 million shares, against 162.49
